<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="comfort-vt">comfort <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kʌmfət/    美 /'kʌmfərt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>安慰；慰藉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My teacher comforted me, saying “Don’t worry. You can do better next time.”
老师安慰我说：“别担心，下次你会做得更好。”</p><footer>2008 浙江</footer></div></div>